BARTER: Negotiating a better price

Category: Trade
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Haggling: talking a seller down or a buyer up from their opening
price. A general negotiating skill useful anywhere goods change
hands, from a legitimate shop counter to a black market deal.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, appraise goods, black market
